title: Abslom Daak, Dalek Killer (1990)
description:
I don't have a clue as to where I got this torrent from.  Labeled as being from the old Demonoid site so....

This appears to be a reissue of the back up story from Doctor Who Weekly Issues 17-20.

Description: The Daleks: in the twenty-sixth century, their very name strikes terror into the hearts of billions across the galaxy. Encased in their metal shells, driven by an unrelenting quest for power, their sole aim is domination of the entire universe!

Abslom Daak - Dalek Killer: a condemned murderer, set against the Dalek race in a vicious guerrilla war by a war-weary Earth empire.

The Daleks: cold-blooded, driven by hatred.

Abslom Daak: driven by blood lust and a death wish.

When chain sword meets polycarbide armor, the results are devastating...
